，不明白她為何仍會成為目標，「着咗褲都睇到咩呢？"},{"pid":"25c6a29cfb21b933d041e7491d48ac7888adf3bb","tid":252844,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T02:02:29.000Z","msg":"亦有網民質疑，片中女士已穿上緊身褲，不明白她為何仍會成為目標，「着咗褲都睇到咩呢？<br />\n<br />\ndasdasa最愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7a8776b5cceadd4af8cfe29747ea34271f41324","tid":252844,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T02:19:55.000Z","msg":"dasdasa"},{"pid":"81a227358bba40798efff0e69a33729feae9f9ae","tid":252844,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T02:20:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>dasdasa</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf719b1d2c433b5eb1d79a83cd0f5daded977af2","tid":252844,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T02:21:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>dasdasa</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c53574e89ef69f99b712424964b4358852899e0","tid":252844,"uid":3549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T02:26:05.000Z","msg":"王心淩"},{"pid":"8e562e159c61c02f65b988f09b57bb5aa510a13d","tid":252844,"uid":54747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T02:29:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>亦有網民質疑，片中女士已穿上緊身褲，不明白她為何仍會成為目標，「着咗褲都睇到咩呢？<br />\n<br />\ndasdasa最愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但佢是做代客泊車，唔是做廚房wor"},{"pid":"be8b262e4fad58adf3eee015bb06b1ff07569379","tid":252844,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T02:35:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>亦有網民質疑，片中女士已穿上緊身褲，不明白她為何仍會成為目標，「着咗褲都睇到咩呢？<br />\n<br />\ndasdasa最愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但佢是做代客泊車